        options: ["Physical restraints and haloperidol","Aggressive cooling + high-dose IV benzodiazepines + IV crystalloid resuscitation — hyperthermia is immediately life-threatening and rhabdomyolysis requires volume resuscitation","Acetaminophen for fever","Observation with frequent vital sign checks"],
